stimulus:
On this round, please imagine that you are playing with a group of:
your acquaintances.

The target value for this round is:
1/4 or 25%.

Please adjust the slider below to enter the value between 0 and 100 that you think would be equal to 1/4 or 25% of the average of what a group of your acquaintances would guess.

On this round, please imagine that you are playing with a group of:
complete strangers.

The target value for this round is:
3/4 or 75%.

Please adjust the slider below to enter the value between 0 and 100 that you think would be equal to 3/4 or 75% of the average of what a group of complete strangers would guess.

On this round, please imagine that you are playing with a group of:
your high school classmates.

The target value for this round is:
2/3 or 67%.

Please adjust the slider below to enter the value between 0 and 100 that you think would be equal to 2/3 or 67% of the average of what a group of your high school classmates would guess.

On this round, please imagine that you are playing with a group of:
your closest friends.

The target value for this round is:
1/3 or 33%.

Please adjust the slider below to enter the value between 0 and 100 that you think would be equal to 1/3 or 33% of the average of what a group of your closest friends would guess.

On this round, please imagine that you are playing with a group of:
other prolific workers.

The target value for this round is:
1/2 or 50%.

Please adjust the slider below to enter the value between 0 and 100 that you think would be equal to 1/2 or 50% of the average of what a group of other prolific workers would guess.
